- body_class 'demos'

%h1 Demos

%section
  %h1 Basic setup
  %p
    Use
    = link_to "the GUI", "/", target: '_blank'
    to setup images and meshes. Then simply create new Morpher object using JSON code exported from GUI.

  .demo#demo1
    .preview
      .controls
        %button{title: 'Play'}
          .play.icon
        %input{type: "range", min: 0, max: 1, step: 0.01, value: 0}
    :javascript
      $('#demo1').each(function() {
